        <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;head/&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;p&gt;Formerly named: Keep Tokens&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Keep Tags is what allows you to prevent tags from randomizing when shuffle captions is selected as well as preventing tags from being dropped out during tag dropout. It is recommended to use Protected Tags File as a better alternative since it won't prevent shuffling of tags like Keep Tags does&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
       </property>
       <property name="text">
